title: stranger_pre
---
<<set $context = "uncertain">>

You sit together in a dim space. Neither of you fully committed to being here.

-> $c2: "We don't have to do anything."
    <<set $tone = "safe">>
    <<jump stranger_start>>

-> $c2: "I think I want this."
    <<set $tone = "forward">>
    <<jump stranger_start>>

-> $c2: "This is kind of weird, huh?"
    <<set $tone = "honest">>
    <<jump stranger_start>>
===

title: stranger_start
---
They smile, a little nervously.

<<fade_out>>
<<jump stranger_act>>
===

title: stranger_act
---
Close proximity. Shared space. Uncertain rhythm.

-> $c2: Mirror their pace
    <<set $sync += 2>>
    <<set $presence += 1>>
    "You adjust carefully, matching them."

-> $c2: Move quickly
    <<set $sync -= 1>>
    <<set $presence -= 1>>
    "You feel slightly out of sync."

-> $c2: Pause, make eye contact
    <<set $sync += 0>>
    <<set $presence += 2>>
    "A quiet moment stretches between you."

-> $c2: Make a joke
    <<set $sync += 1>>
    <<set $presence += 0>>
    "They laugh, tension shifting."

===

title: stranger_post
---
<<fade_in>>

You both sit there for a moment after.

-> $c2: "That was nice."
    <<set $emotional_outcome += 1>>
    "They nod, but seem unsure what it meant."

-> $c2: "We should do this again."
    <<set $emotional_outcome += 0>>
    "They smile politely."

-> $c2: "Sorry, that was awkward."
    <<set $emotional_outcome -= 1>>
    "They look relieved... or maybe distant."

===
